name: Officer D.Va ( う-´)づ/̵͇̿̿/’̿’̿ ̿ ̿̿ ̿̿  (LoRA)
description:
Henlo (✿◠ᴗ◠)づ !!! Officer D.Va on duty ∠(^ー^) ! Btw please recommend more skins from video games you’d like to see !! I’m kind of in a drought of things to make Lora’s of !!

Requested by @SonGoku thank you so much for the request !! I really appreciate it ( ˘͈ ᵕ ˘͈♡)

((This Lora does work for photorealistic models sorta for once hehe))

This Lora works with almost every anime model and semi realistic models !! so go wild with it !! ^^

Please use negative prompt Embedding bad-image-v2-39000 it works a lot better then without it !! I've noticed many issues with odd poses soo this will help that !!

use trigger words female_service_cap, pink_facial_mark, brown_eyes, if your having trouble getting all her features and clothing !

Please use Trigger words ((naked)), (nude), nipples if your having issues with getting good NSFW generations (specifically with her breast not having nipples) <3

This Lora also works really well in combination with other Lora's so have fun with that !!

I recommend keeping the weight at (0.7-1) and using the negative prompts as needed !!

I had so much fun making the Lora and generating the images I hope you have as much fun as I did ⸜(｡˃ ᵕ ˂ )⸝♡ !!!

Please be kind with this Lora ♡

modelVersions.name: Officer_D.va_V1
modelVersions.description:
I highly recommend using the trigger word Officer_DVa.

I also highly recommend keeping the weight between (0.7-1) and using negative prompts where needed !

Please use negative prompt Embedding bad-image-v2-39000 it works a lot better then without it !!

use trigger words female_service_cap, brown_eyes, pink_facial_mark, if your having trouble getting all her features and clothing !

Here are all the settings used for most the examples:

Size: 512x512

Clip skip: 2

Hires upscale: 2

Hires upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B

Discard penultimate sigma: True

If you have any issues please tell me and ill try and help !! ૮₍ ˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶ ₎ა
